headline: International Paper CEO to Speak at Baird 2025 Global Industrial Conference
summary: International Paper Chief Executive Officer Andy Silvernail will speak at the Baird 2025 Global Industrial Conference on Tuesday, November 11, 2025. The presentation is scheduled to begin at 9:30 a.m. ET (8:30 a.m. CT) and will be followed by a question-and-answer session.
